Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.31,0:00:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this one?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.27,0:00:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this one is better.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.38,0:00:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, I'm tired of this.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.85,0:00:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I choose this.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.98,0:00:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm going\N to show this to anyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.96,0:01:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.93,0:01:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How come no man seems to notice \Nthis beautiful body?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.31,0:01:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm more than ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.16,0:01:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.96,0:01:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I've no time for this.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.48,0:01:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.25,0:01:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So trendy! But of course! \NMy sense of fashion is impeccable.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.38,0:01:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.05,0:01:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.49,0:01:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Miki. Behave yourself, okay? {? dunno what she means: no rudeness okay}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.46,0:01:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.33,0:01:50.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm Miki. I entered college last spring.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,Where am I going?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.29,0:01:53.33,Thought,,0,0,0,,Just to work.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.33,0:01:54.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm a hardworking girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.25,0:02:01.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to help the son of my mom's friend study during the winter break.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.11,0:02:02.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,It's a single parent household. {single mother}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.94,0:02:08.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,And because the mother is too busy with work and housework to help her son study,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.22,0:02:11.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,she asked me to help\N her son with his studies.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.45,0:02:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.46,0:02:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, my boots got dirty. {there's a saying in japanese that a ripened persimmon falls into the mouth of the one who's waiting, so maybe this whole scene with persimmons is some kind of allusion to that}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.40,0:02:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.72,0:02:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.20,0:02:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.89,0:02:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm concerned that his grades \Nhave dropped lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a guest right now,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.15,0:02:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.65,0:02:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.91,0:02:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.67,0:02:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"A guest," she says.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.82,0:02:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what it's called these days?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate him.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.96,0:03:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.82,0:03:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.09,Thought,,0,0,0,,I can see it's not "nothing."
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.16,0:03:14.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,What an unfriendly kid. {unlikeable}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, I'm bored.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.02,0:03:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you wanna see\N something interesting?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.09,0:03:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What's interesting?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to keep quiet, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.09,0:03:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.49,0:03:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.85,0:03:55.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.45,0:03:57.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,That brat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.49,0:04:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.45,0:04:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not scary, is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.07,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.85,0:09:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.23,0:09:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.61,0:09:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miss Miki.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.58,0:10:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.31,0:10:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.51,0:10:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do all adults do that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.98,0:10:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.49,0:10:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop thinking about that \Nand finish your studying already!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're blushing!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.33,0:10:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were thinking something like that too!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.31,0:11:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, tell me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.07,0:11:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it feel good?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.56,0:11:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you done it before?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.18,0:11:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut that out, or I'll get mad!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.38,0:11:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are your private parts also yucky like my mom's?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.60,0:11:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.89,0:11:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine is still clean!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.89,0:11:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you want to see if mine looks like your mom's?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.32,0:11:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't tell anyone about this, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.99,0:11:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What if your mom comes in?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. She won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.23,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When she has her "guest,"\N she doesn't come here until 5:30.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.77,0:12:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we have an hour\N and twenty minutes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to look carefully.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.03,0:12:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.79,0:13:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it look?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.52,0:13:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a little different.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.47,0:13:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Different {\i1}how{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.12,0:13:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know how to answer that...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.52,0:13:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Look... Look closely.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.81,0:13:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I still can't see the shape.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.01,0:13:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It does look different from mom's.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.63,0:14:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you have to be more specific.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.10,0:14:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the outer vulva. \NThen what's this? {labia majora}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.14,0:14:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The inner lips. {labia minora​}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.95,0:14:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be cleaner than your mom's.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.64,0:14:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't really tell.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything looks all mixed up.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the clitoris.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right? You got that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine isn't dirty like your mom's.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.20,0:14:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come closer and keep looking \Nuntil you can see the difference.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.17,0:14:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so wet that I can't see clearly.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go ahead and clean it up.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something dirty.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.58,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is where your pee comes out.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.17,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.79,0:14:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.61,0:14:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up. We don't have much time.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.37,0:15:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... doing well.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.43,0:15:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can... You can stop now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.91,0:15:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not a bit cleaner.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.19,0:16:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's even wetter,\N and I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Stop that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.12,0:16:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move your fingers! Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.55,0:17:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my turn now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.78,0:17:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? N-No!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.46,0:17:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.35,0:17:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They might hear us \Nfrom downstairs if you yell.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.69,0:17:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.39,0:18:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.12,0:18:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you feel good soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.15,0:19:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Did you like it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.99,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.23,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.01,0:20:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.03,0:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wonder why he closed the curtain.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.12,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so he could focus better?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.35,0:20:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little earlier than usual, \Nbut I guess I can take up some tea now.
